These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, security-guard, accountant
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, garlic, potato
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, iced-tea
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the freelancer is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the person drinking water is on the right of the security-guard##1
5. the person eating potato is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Job         | security-guard | freelancer   | accountant   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| Food   | potato  | broccoli    | garlic      |
| Beverage     | fanta     | water      | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, july, april
House: farmhouse, modern, ranch-style
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, skateboard, ship
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the ranch-style house##1
4. the person eating kale is the modern house##1
5. the person driving the trike is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Birthday   | july     | april     | may      |
| House   | ranch-style  | modern | farmhouse |
| Transport           | ship | trike     | skateboard       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, dubstep, soul
House: cottage, ranch-style, tower
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, writing, reading
1. the cottage house is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the tower house and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is the fan of dubstep##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre          | hip-hop  | soul     | dubstep     |
| House           | tower | cottage  | ranch-style   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| Hobby           | reading     | gardening | writing |

