.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, skateboard, jet-ski
3 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, billiard
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, daffodil, aconite
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person playing backgammon and the person who growsazalea##2
4. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Transport    | tram       | jet-ski  | skateboard   |
| Game     | backgammon    | billiard  | scrabble |
| Flower     | daffodil   | aconite | azalea        |
| Sport   | snowboarding | rowing     | rugby      |

