The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, tennis, baseball
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Flower          | amaryllis    | rose     | orchid      |
| Hobby         | cooking | filmmaking | photography |
| Birthday   | july  | march       | june       |
| Sport           | tennis     | rowing       | baseball     |

