.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, badminton, lacrosse
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, sudoku
City: rome, miami, prague
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, car, ship
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person traveling to miami is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person driving the car##2
4. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Sport          | badminton | tennis | lacrosse    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku      | filmmaking |
| City   | rome   | miami     | prague        |
| Transport           | quad-bike      | ship       | car      |

