The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, handball, skiing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, western
House: cape-cod, art-deco, townhouse
1. the art-deco house is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's birthday is in december and the cape-cod house##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person watching comedy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Birthday          | december      | july   | march |
| Sport         | sailing | handball | skiing |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | western | fantasy   |
| House     | townhouse         | art-deco  | cape-cod       |

