.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, swisher, game
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, horse-climbing
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, strawberry, asparagus
3 different pets are kept: hamster, goat, horse
1. the person eating asparagus is on the far left##1
2. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person eating pineapple is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the game-smoker##2
5. the swisher-smoker is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Cigar      | baccarat       | swisher      | game      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | horse-climbing | chess      |
| Food           | asparagus | pineapple     | strawberry |
| Pet   | goat     | horse          | hamster       |

