The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, august, november
1. the person who's birthday is in november is between the security-guard and the teacher##2
2. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
5. the designer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | almond-milk | cola     |
| Flower          | sunflower   | poppy      | rose     |
| Job   | teacher  | designer      | security-guard |
| Birthday     | march | november        | august     |

