1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the fan of rock is between the fan of ambient and the person who's birthday is in april##2
3. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is the fan of funk##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
6. the person driving the roller is the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Birthday       | april       | may       | november    |
| Music-Genre         | funk | rock | ambient |
| Cigar       | tiparillo      | bluemaster         | game |
| Transport   | roller        | taxi            | scooter  |

