.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, daffodil, sunflower
House: wooden, cottage, victorian
3 different games are played: backgammon, go, monopoly
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, italian
1. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person playing go##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the italian##1
3. the indonesian is in the middle##1
4. the indonesian is between the cottage house and the wooden house##2
5. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
6. the wooden house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Flower      | sunflower     | daffodil | azalea      |
| House         | cottage  | victorian       | wooden |
| Game   | monopoly   | go         | backgammon     |
| Nationality   | american | indonesian    | italian     |

