.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, snooker
3 different pets are kept: snake, hamster, cat
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, musical, sports
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, handball, water-polo
1. the person playing billiard is the owner of the cat##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
5. the person playing billiard is between the owner of the hamster and the person watching musical movies##2
6. the person watching horror movies is the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Game      | backgammon | billiard      | snooker            |
| Pet           | snake | cat | hamster |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | sports        | horror         |
| Sport   | handball  | ice-hockey    | water-polo        |

