3. the police-officer is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
5. the person playing monopoly is the craftsman house##1
6. the coach is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
