City: edinburgh, prague, rome
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, nigerian, spanish
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, hot-chocolate
1. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the nigerian##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is between the person traveling to rome and the spanish##2
3. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person traveling to rome and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
5. the person traveling to prague is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby          | hiking  | sudoku   | card-games |
| City   | rome  | prague     | edinburgh |
| Nationality   | chinese | nigerian | spanish   |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate   | mirinda   | milk      |

