.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-16::.
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, indian, indonesian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, funk, metal
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, aquamarine, ivory
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, tram
1. the fan of funk is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the fan of metal is between the person driving the boat and the fan of gospel##2
3. the indonesian is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is the person driving the boat##1
5. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the turkish##1
6. the turkish is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Nationality       | indonesian | turkish | indian |
| Music-Genre         | gospel   | metal       | funk        |
| Color       | ivory | turquise   | aquamarine         |
| Transport   | tram    | train     | boat         |

