3. the person eating avocado is the modern house##1
4. the lawyer is on the left of the person eating peach##1
5. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
6. the writer is between the engineer and the person who likes emerald##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Job           | lawyer   | writer   | engineer |
| Food   | avocado | peach   | broccoli     |
| Color   | emerald     | coral      | orange    |
| House           | modern | wooden | cape-cod    |

