.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, spinach, strawberry
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite, almond-milk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bongani, dunhill
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, gardening, board-games
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
2. the person drinking sprite is the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the bongani-smoker is the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the game-smoker is the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the bongani-smoker##2
6. the dunhill-smoker is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | spinach      | raspberry | strawberry |
| Beverage         | sprite     | almond-milk    | tea        |
| Cigar       | bongani | dunhill   | game   |
| Hobby   | baking          | gardening     | board-games       |

 